protein.general_function: Involved in G-protein coupled receptor protein signaling pathway
protein.specific_function: Receptor for prostaglandin F2-alpha (PGF2-alpha). The activity of this receptor is mediated by G proteins which activate a phosphatidylinositol-calcium second messenger system. Initiates luteolysis in the corpus luteum

go_class.description: cell surface receptor linked signaling pathway
g-protein coupled receptor protein signaling pathway
